      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>YTForge was born out of a simple idea: to make YouTube tools accessible, reliable, and user-friendly for creators of all levels. We know how challenging it can be to manage, analyze, and optimize content on YouTube—so we created a platform to make that process easier.</p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>Our mission is to support digital creators by offering fast, free, and effective tools that help with everything from video downloading to metadata extraction, tag analysis, copyright awareness, and monetization checking. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned creator, YTForge is here to back your journey.</p>

      <h2>Why YTForge?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Fast & Simple Tools:</strong> No clutter. Just clean interfaces and instant results.</li>
        <li><strong>Creator-Centric:</strong> Everything we build is designed with your growth in mind.</li>
        <li><strong>Free Access:</strong> We believe that powerful tools should be available to everyone, not just professionals.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
      <p>We're a small group of developers, content creators, and tech enthusiasts who are passionate about digital freedom and creativity. We use the tools we build—and we build them better every day based on real user feedback.</p>
    </section>

